        "25% of audit duration lost",
        "Internal procedure in progress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一阶段\"Initial Negotiations and Blockers\"已经整理好了。现在看第二阶段，代码接收部分——10月27日先收到了Education_StudentDB的.NET 3.1代码，但Matching Engine是黑盒？",
      "elements_involved": [
